grpcStatusCodes.UNAVAILABLE: Cloud Fleet Routing is not available at the moment. Please try again later (gRPC error 14).
grpcStatusCodes.ALREADY_EXISTS: Your client attempted to create something that already exists (gRPC error 6).
grpcStatusCodes.CANCELLED: The Cloud Fleet Routing request was cancelled (gRPC error 1).
grpcStatusCodes.DATA_LOSS: Some data was lost or corrupted (gRPC error 15).
grpcStatusCodes.DEADLINE_EXCEEDED: Cloud Fleet Routing didn't come up with a solution. Try increasing the solve time.
grpcStatusCodes.FAILED_PRECONDITION: Some precondition wasn't met, and Cloud Fleet Routing can't continue (gRPC error 9).
grpcStatusCodes.INVALID_ARGUMENT:
Invalid request.
Please refer to the Cloud Fleet Routing documentation.
grpcStatusCodes.NOT_FOUND: Some requested entity couldn't be found (gRPC error 5).
grpcStatusCodes.OUT_OF_RANGE: Some operation was attempted outside a valid range (gRPC error 11).
grpcStatusCodes.PERMISSION_DENIED: Your client doesn't have permission to use Cloud Fleet Routing. See the Cloud Fleet Routing setup instructions.
grpcStatusCodes.RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED: Some resource has been exhausted (gRPC error 8).
grpcStatusCodes.UNAUTHENTICATED: The request doesn't have valid authentication credentials. See the Cloud Fleet Routing setup instructions.
